data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom/3 bathroom split floor plan family home on a large corner lot fully fenced , located in the lovely southeast neighborhood of Willow Oaks! With BRAND NEW ROOF JUST INSTALLED (AUG 2023). The kitchen features lots of cabinets for storage and new stainless steel appliances ! The home also comes with a BRAND NEW WATER HEATER. There is an eat-in kitchen area with a beautiful functioning fireplace and a formal dining room as well. The living room feels very open with its high ceilings. There are sliding glass doors that let in all the natural light and lead out to your big newly screened in  lanai featuring multiple ceiling fans, that are perfect to enjoy the shade in the hot summer. Attached to the lanai is a full pool bathroom with a shower for when you are hosting at your large in-ground saltwater swimming pool. This home also features a 2 car garage and carport/ boat that leads up to a workshop that has electricity ! Along the side of the house are also RV hookups.YOU DON"T MISS OUT ON THIS HOME
